- python.gen

You can inject python scripts, define your own functions, etc. See below for syntax.

@run {
    @python {
        # By default, math.* and random have been imported.

        def roll_dice(sides=6):
            return rint(1, sides)
    }

    @loop 5 {
        roll: roll_dice()
    }
    \n
}

Example output:
5 1 6 6 1 
